quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  25,12,"Itha raat-hum min makaninbaAAeedin samiAAoo laha taghayyuthanwazafeera"
  25,13,"Wa-itha olqoo minha makanandayyiqan muqarraneena daAAaw hunalika thuboora"
  25,14,"La tadAAoo alyawma thubooran wahidanwadAAoo thubooran katheera"
  25,15,"Qul athalika khayrun am jannatualkhuldi allatee wuAAida almuttaqoona kanat lahum jazaanwamaseera"
  25,16,"Lahum feeha ma yashaoonakhalideena kana AAala rabbika waAAdanmas-oola"
  25,17,"Wayawma yahshuruhum wamayaAAbudoona min dooni Allahi fayaqoolu aantum adlaltumAAibadee haola-i am hum dalloo assabeel"
  25,18,"Qaloo subhanaka ma kanayanbaghee lana an nattakhitha min doonika min awliyaawalakin mattaAAtahum waabaahum hattanasoo aththikra wakanoo qawman boora"
  25,19,"Faqad kaththabookum bimataqooloona fama tastateeAAoona sarfan walanasran waman yathlim minkum nuthiqhuAAathaban kabeera"
  25,20,"Wama arsalna qablaka minaalmursaleena illa innahum laya/kuloona attaAAamawayamshoona fee al-aswaqi wajaAAalna baAAdakumlibaAAdin fitnatan atasbiroona wakanarabbuka baseera"
